allStalls.name: Jin Ji Fish Soup Ban Mian

information.moreAboutThisHawker: Relatively new stall but does some delicious ban mian. Soup is super flavourful and free-flow spring onions also helps. The owner is a nice and generous guy and I used to always eat ban mian as a post-workout meal. Highly reccommend the dry you mian with their chilli, does not dissapoint.
